; Regression test for variable capture in fusion renaming.
; Star A's R must become 5 (via t), star B's R must become 7 (via u).
; Both stars name their local variable R: after they merge, the
; renaming must keep the two variables distinct.
(show (exec
  {[(-a) (+t R) (o1 R)]
   [(-b) (+u R) (o2 R)]
   [(-t 5)]
   [(-u 7)]}
  [(+a) (+b)]))
